---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Four clinics, one standard of care | AymanCare Blog"
  description="Primary care, urgent care, and pediatrics across Dallas, North Richland Hills, Mesquite, and Valley Ranch — the same board-certified standard at every…"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/blog/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Four clinics, one standard of care\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/blog/four-clinics-one-team/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/blog/">Blog</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Four Clinics, One Standard</span>
  </div>
  <span class="overline fade-in">◆ AymanCare Locations · Dallas–Fort Worth</span>
  <h1 class="page-title fade-in">Four clinics,<br>one <em>standard of care.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle fade-in">Primary care, urgent care, and pediatrics across Dallas, North Richland Hills, Mesquite, and Valley Ranch — the same board-certified standard at every location.</p>
</section>
<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 100px;">
  <div style="max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.8;">
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 01</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;">Dallas — <em>N Buckner Blvd</em> · East Dallas · Lake Highlands</h3>
      <p>AymanCare's Dallas location on North Buckner Boulevard is our original clinic — serving the East Dallas, Lake Highlands, and Lakewood communities since the beginning. It offers the full range of primary care, walk-in urgent care, and pediatric services. Patients from East Dallas, Old East Dallas, and surrounding neighborhoods choose this clinic for board-certified family medicine with same-day availability. Walk-ins welcome. Medicare, Tricare, and most major insurance accepted.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 02</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;">North Richland Hills — <em>Mid-Cities DFW</em> · Hurst · Bedford · Euless</h3>
      <p>AymanCare's North Richland Hills clinic serves the Mid-Cities corridor — one of the most densely populated parts of the DFW metroplex. Families in Hurst, Euless, Bedford, Colleyville, and Keller have access to primary care, allergy treatment, medical weight loss, and same-day urgent care without driving into Dallas or Fort Worth. Board-certified care. Short wait times. Same insurance accepted as our other DFW locations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 03</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;">Mesquite — <em>I-30 East</em> · Balch Springs · Sunnyvale</h3>
      <p>The AymanCare Mesquite clinic on I-30 East brings board-certified primary care and urgent care to the eastern suburbs of Dallas. Patients from Mesquite, Balch Springs, Sunnyvale, and Forney have a trusted family medicine option close to home. Evening hours make it practical for working families. All services — primary care, flu and COVID testing, allergy treatment, and pediatric visits — are available here, with the same clinical standards as every AymanCare location.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 04</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;">Valley Ranch — <em>Irving</em> · Las Colinas · Coppell</h3>
      <p>AymanCare's Valley Ranch location in Irving serves the Las Colinas corridor and neighboring communities including Coppell, Carrollton, and Grand Prairie. It's our newest clinic — and it brings the same physician-led primary care, urgent care, and pediatric services to a fast-growing part of the DFW metroplex. Walk-ins welcome. Same board-certified physicians, same insurance plans, same 4.8-star standard.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 05</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;">What <em>stays the same</em> at every Dallas-area AymanCare</h3>
      <p>Every AymanCare location across Dallas–Fort Worth is staffed by board-certified physicians, accepts Medicare, Tricare, Aetna, BlueCross, Cigna, UnitedHealth, and Humana, and follows the same clinical protocols. Your records transfer seamlessly between any of our four DFW clinics. There are no different tiers of care for different neighborhoods — the same standard you'd find in East Dallas is what you'll find in North Richland Hills, Mesquite, and Irving.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="neighborhood-band fade-in" style="margin-top: 60px;">
      <div>
        <span class="overline" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;">✦ Serving Dallas–Fort Worth</span>
        <h2>Find your nearest<br><em>AymanCare clinic.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Serving East Dallas, Lake Highlands, North Richland Hills (Mid-Cities), Mesquite (I-30 E), and Valley Ranch in Irving. Same-day appointments. Walk-ins welcome. Board-certified care at every location.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent">Book appointment →</a>
          <a href="/locations/" class="btn btn-ghost">View all locations ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
